1.3.0.name: wordpress/buzzea-shopping-guide
1.3.0.description:
En Français: Faites profiter votre lectorat d'un outil paramétrable de comparaison de prix et monétisez l'audience de ces pages au CPC.

Create Shopping Guides / Pages / Shopping Banners to install on your site. Monetize your audience via CPC (cost per click).

Shopping Guides / Pages / Shopping Banners

How it works:

  • You get paid for clicks on products in your Shopping Guide / banners
  • Choose from 2 themes
  • Choose colours to suit your site
  • Choose a name for your shopping guide
  • Choose your favourite categories
  • Choose your favourite products
  • Choose banners for your site (5 sizes available, more soon!)
  • Fully customisable
  • Français/English available
